  85:../Middlewares/threadx/common/src/tx_thread_initialize.c **** /* Define the priority map active bit map that specifies which of the previously 
  86:../Middlewares/threadx/common/src/tx_thread_initialize.c ****    defined priority maps have something set. This is only necessary if more than 
